author: Gordon R. Friedman | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Kate Brown to Greg Walden: Don't kill progress made under Affordable Care Act
text: Gov. Kate Brown met with U.S. Rep. Greg Walden, R-Ore., Monday afternoon at his Capitol Hill office to lobby the congressman on preserving health care benefits granted under Affordable Care Act.
